@zakimar
I honestly really liked this movie with him as the main actor. Admittedly I think its a bit funny that hes like 20 or something and his voice is high pitched but apart from that this movie is honestly in my top 3 movies which is pretty good IMO. And Seth Rogen? Are you serious? I think the producer made a pretty swell decision for the actors.

For everyone who wants to know how good the movie is, I would honestly say it is worth downloading ATLEAST. This movie doesn't deserve half the negative comments its getting. Loved it and I've watched it 10 times over, probably more. 8/10 for me tbh.
